    <p>Pesta Buku Me­layu Sin­ga­pura 2020 (Singapore Malay Book Fair 2020) re­turns for a sec­ond year but will go on­line. It is com­mis­sioned by #BuySingLit with the sup­port of the Na­tional Arts Coun­cil and part­nered with Wisma Gey­lang Serai. Event high­lights in­clude chef Roszi­lah M. Nor’s kueh-mak­ing ses­sion to ac­com­pany the sto­ry­telling ses­sion of Apa Nama Kuih Ini?, a chil­dren’s pic­ture book re­cently shortliste­d for Best Pic­ture Book at the Singapore Book Awards 2020. View­ers also stand to win #BuySingLit e-vouch­ers. WHERE: Face­book pages of Pesta Buku Me­layu Sin­ga­pura (all events) and Wisma Gey­lang Serai (se­lected events) WHEN: Sun - Sept 18, 8.30 - 10pm; Sept 19 & 20, 11am - 9.30pm AD­MIS­SION: Free ad­mis­sion un­less oth­er­wise stated</p>
    <p>INFO: bit.ly/2ReXeYB</p>


